Id
Email

john@example.com


2

方法：使用 DELETE 和 WHERE 子句
我们可以使用以下代码，将此表与它自身在电子邮箱列中连接起来。
SELECT p1.*
FROM Person p1,
    Person p2
WHERE
    p1.Email = p2.Email
;

FROM Person p1,
    Person p2
WHERE
    p1.Email = p2.Email AND p1.Id > p2.Id
;

    Person p2
